  "keyFeatures": [
    "Visual web editor with real-time collaboration and Git sync",
    "AI agent that writes and maintains docs via pull requests",
    "Interactive API playground from OpenAPI specifications",
    "AI assistant embedded in docs for user Q&A",
    "Automations for scheduled and event-triggered doc updates",
    "Custom themes, fonts, and domain configuration",
    "Role-based access control and SSO (Enterprise)",
    "CLI for local preview, validation, and broken-link checks",
    "MCP server and llms.txt for AI tool discoverability",
    "Integrations with Slack, Notion, Linear, Jira, and more"
